Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.62,0:00:39.43,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是誰 對未來都著著一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:47.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝著明天大步邁進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.11,0:00:57.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}總有一天會覺醒的 真實心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.89,0:01:03.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}現在就伸出雙手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.06,0:01:13.90,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在這開始變化的世界 立刻前往探尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:19.84,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牽繫著你的手絕不再分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因為有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.08,0:01:27.52,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找尋的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.02,0:01:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「第九話  唯你讓我心動」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.29,0:01:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字是善行忠孝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.46,0:01:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為5121部隊的司令官 也擔任班上的班長一職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.90,0:01:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本職務需要沉著冷靜的決策力 以及迅速的執行能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.14,0:01:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之所以必須要將其銘記於心 務必完成達到這樣的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.38,0:01:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為我的任何判斷 都將左右部下們珍貴的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.38,0:02:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.55,0:02:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休息一下會比較有效率的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.12,0:02:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠阪圭吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然被稱為含著金湯匙出生 可說是貴族世家的後繼者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但卻自願入伍服役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個有能力且冷靜的左右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 請等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.74,0:02:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若宮康光、來須銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.35,0:02:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們負責隨隊步兵的工作 也是HWT駕駛員訓練教官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.85,0:02:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於職務有著熱情跟矜持 可說是非常難得的人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託不要把這個飛車吃掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字是原素子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.66,0:02:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果把怪人集結的5121部隊比喻成一個猴子軍團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼猴老大就是司令官善行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而統管娘子軍的母猴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.77,0:03:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更正 美麗的領袖就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.78,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這是在學誰說話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.28,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之所以叫做娘子軍 是因為整備小組只有女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於人手不足 通宵作業是家常便飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機油或化學藥物的使用也是肌膚的大敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要休息一下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的點心是蘋果派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常好吃喔～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.41,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.74,0:03:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,森精華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.14,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像小狗般粘著我的可愛學妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.75,0:03:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.88,0:03:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是本日派遣到5121部隊整備小組的森精華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫原素子 請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才要請您多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不擅長跟人往來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜歡機械！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.04,0:04:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為只要注入愛情 機械就一定會回報你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.88,0:04:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 我喜歡機械 也喜歡人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.39,0:04:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊真紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.33,0:04:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出生在不幸之星 5121部隊的不幸少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.47,0:04:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次去神社抽籤 只知道大兇內容為何的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊好慢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是今天入隊的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是早就要到了才對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起、對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.49,0:04:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起、對不起、對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊怎麼了 剛剛怎麼好大一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.27,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在在哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在小道市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於我搭的電車出事 很抱歉會晚點抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你自己沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-是的 托您的福\N-糟糕 那是汽油車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊怎麼了？田邊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.23,0:05:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到兩個月之後 她才來到了5121部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜歡蘋果的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看 好像很好吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪上久臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然平常吊兒郎當 但軍中經歷卻是無法想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被認為是高深莫測的一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芳野春香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們班擔任一般科目的導師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.06,0:06:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於她的個性 大家都直接叫她春香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都看不出比我們大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀨戶口隆之、瀧川陽平 他們是HWT的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.14,0:06:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加藤祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.71,0:06:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從經理、總務到雜用一手包辦 自稱萬能的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是熊本出生 但說話卻是關西腔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一毛不差 我果然是天才啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.02,0:06:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼帳簿在哪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.86,0:06:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東原望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啟動PBE時不可或缺的人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.23,0:06:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然軍隊跟小孩的組合很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.17,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但她的存在卻是5121部隊的潤滑劑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.04,0:06:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水厚志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.48,0:06:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HWT雙人座機型中 負責操縱系統的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.55,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日常生活雖然優柔寡斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在戰場上關於雙人座機型的操縱已有心得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.62,0:07:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟芝村舞的默契也有進步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.69,0:07:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過最近看來訓練成效不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人在意的是芝村舞的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.51,0:07:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然跟部隊成員相處比較好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.01,0:07:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但偶而會看到她表情哀愁 或是在想些心事的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論如何 這是個大問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心中有股陰霾揮散不去對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀨戶口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次跟我約會喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是戀愛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方是小舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別隱瞞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想跟你討論的我真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.18,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是害怕失敗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.95,0:08:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凡事應該做了再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.19,0:08:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論你在煩惱什麼 人生很多事情都來自經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.19,0:08:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試著踏出步伐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試著踏出步伐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.14,0:08:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以進來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼 不也是你自己的房間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.78,0:08:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以問一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.05,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天天氣真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.16,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是 天氣好的話也幹得快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.66,0:08:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做模型 看就知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.80,0:09:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你喜歡模型啊 真是不錯的興趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的興趣是園藝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時期牽牛花很棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是藍色的 真的很漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.08,0:09:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼有點怪怪的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 像這麼自然就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.19,0:09:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凡事應該做了再說 原來是這種涵意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？到底是啥啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 瀧川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.50,0:09:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得我抓到要領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.31,0:09:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我無可取代的好友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想應該已經接吻了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舞最近都若有所思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.85,0:09:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定在去年的聖誕節就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道已經那個了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讓人不好意思呢～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「那個」是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到「那個」就是那個囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要繼續說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.37,0:10:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 在困境中萌芽的愛情 據說都不會長久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別潑冷水啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.37,0:10:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該溫暖地守護年輕男女的既成事實啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是既成事實嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再說了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既成事實是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不說明也沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.63,0:10:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過速水跟芝村配對的話 那就是金龜婿的女生版呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.87,0:10:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金龜婿是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.80,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如我跟遠阪結婚 就等於是嫁給金龜婿喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊真正喜歡的是遠阪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是舉例啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以小志要嫁給小舞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有些不一樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之就當成是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.43,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為「既成的事實」 所以成為小志的金龜婿好棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在亂教小孩子什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.48,0:11:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況那種人不是我喜歡的類型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.55,0:11:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凡事隨便又懦弱悶騷 根本就是優柔寡斷的範本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.42,0:11:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算全世界剩下他一個男的 我也不會多看他一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.86,0:11:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是因為工作 我根本不會跟他進駕駛艙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒起步就踩空了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是來關心長嶺女高的資料吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.26,0:12:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你之前不是還想追芝村嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做事是往前看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有注意他們兩人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然 訓練數值一直在下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是指什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只會對數字有興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.18,0:13:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒發覺他們最近特意疏遠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是被這種無聊感情所困啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.65,0:13:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無聊…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.65,0:13:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰場上只需要友情 不是愛情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能分別愛情跟友情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在對你也只有友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是別吵了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要用我的方法來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使我說不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.83,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為任務以外的事情而分心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招致自己遭遇危險是愚蠢至極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務以外？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽清楚了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.85,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天接受訓練 跟搭檔培養默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼此共同努力的話 所有事情都可以順心如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.12,0:14:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.86,0:14:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要作好駕駛員的工作就行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要工作順利的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將會解決你所有的煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要擺出這麼可怕的表惰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請告訴我叫我來這的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.39,0:15:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從以前就覺得你很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要亂說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是開什麼玩笑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟壬生屋一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.31,0:15:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叫著「真是不純潔」 而且憤怒得滿臉通紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.71,0:15:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是笨呢 其實不會不純潔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你害怕會後悔嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時連後悔都沒辦法喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對自己坦誠一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是要說這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得我抓到要領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.58,0:15:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.59,0:16:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有些話想跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.64,0:16:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.98,0:16:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對自己坦誠一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於我們的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天起工作也要加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.49,0:16:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說的就是這些嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘彈數0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.08,0:17:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊墜率55%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人的數值一直在下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我的建言完全沒有成效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.82,0:17:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村舞努力要無視於速水厚志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.66,0:17:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那番話她沒聽進去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實一點不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說舞跟速水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不是無法理解啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟芝村舞就是那樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.65,0:18:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那由男方主動不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過速水也是個小呆瓜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的看不下去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.86,0:18:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就來揭發真相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.14,0:18:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那照例是一個月的點心\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(戀愛進展大預測)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下注下注！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道選什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經決定囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學姊你怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來 田邊你覺得是哪邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這次也有自信喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.72,0:18:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說啦 快說快說～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我賭的就是這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.75,0:19:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼在這裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.59,0:19:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小美今天想要吃炸蝦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-炸蝦？\N-因為我喜歡吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要吃好多好多
